News

Wednesday March 27th, 2019

Clap of end of Paris 2018 Paris 2018 Annual Report

   par Manuel Picaud

   The final general meeting of Paris 2018 was held on March 23, 2019. All
   resolutions were unanimously adopted. Here is the moral report, which
   concludes in the dissolution of the association whose object is indeed
   finished. A festive evening at the historic partner Who’s has completed
   this very beautiful adventure.

   The General Assembly of Paris 2018 voted unanimously on this moral
   report and unanimously decided to dissolve the association whose
   purpose is over.

